attachments.title: Black Cotton Remixed, Vol.2 (SAMPLER Mini Mix) **FREE DL** by Freshly Squeezed (Record Label)
attachments.text:
Second release in the series that takes tracks from the vintage side of the award-winning White Mink : Black Cotton double CD series. Black Cotton Remixed 2 raises the stakes from Vol 1 with a 5 track EP of brand new Electro Swing. German producer's Wolfgang Lohr and Louie Prima (Electro Swing Elite and Electro Swing Revolution respectively) return with a version of Puttin' On The Ritz while Pisk (better known as the producer behind SWINGROWERS) joins the party with not one, but two fresh remixes, while last but not least, Mista Trick weights in with a little goodness for Drum and Bass heads.

"Freshly Squeezed lay down five more unabashed versions on classic speak easy standards. Highlights include the insane energy and juicy funk of Wolfgang & Louie's "Puttin' On The Ritz", the floor-burning D&B mischief of Mista Trick's "Swinging All Day" and the almost rocky stomp on Pisk's "One Steady Roll". Teases and pleasers with nothing but authentic instrumentation and preemo prohibition party vibes." Juno Download Review
